recommended environment/notes
-----------------------
NOTE-1: I place my devel libs in $HOME/dev/
NOTE-2: changing .profile requires logout/in of current user

requirements to build
------------------------------------
1) 	download from http://freeimage.sourceforge.net download page and unpack 
	NOTE: I'm using FreeImage-3.15.1
2) 	add FREEIMAGE_ROOT export to .profile 
	export FREEIMAGE_ROOT=$HOME/dev/FreeImage-3.15.1
3) change 
	FROM
	#define USE_SETMODE
	TO 
	#undef USE_SETMODE
	 